name: Into The Heart Of African Jungle

metadata.name: Old Hunter With An Ancient Gun
metadata.description:
An old hunter (Ode) from the Yoruba tribe of Nigeria.
 Shows how he prepare his ancient dane gun ( Yoruba call it: ibon Shakabula or ibon ode) for hunting.
 He has been hunting since he was young.
 Hunting is part of his way of life and culture, because it was pass down to him by his father.
His look, fingers, gun, back pack, equipment , dressing all tells a unique story of a great and ancient Nigerian/African hunter.
